Shortly after finishing my bottle of ADG Profumo, I was headed back to the store to find my next bottle. Wanting desperately to find something new and could take the role of my next signature scent, I spent a solid 30 minutes of my time and the very gracious sales attendant. 

I was looking for something masculine, not too mature and not too youthful. I knew I loved the darker aspects of the ADG, so I wanted to find something that was spicy and deep, while staying light and suitable for all day wear. When we got to Prada Luna Rossa Black, it was love at first sniff. Spicy, aromatic, powdery, and deep. This is such a special and unique fragrance.
